        {
            "id": 7,
            "module": "mistral-ai:createACompletion",
            "version": 1,
            "parameters": {
                "__IMTCONN__": 8636051
            },
            "filter": null,
            "mapper": {
                "model": "mistral-medium-2505",
                "messages": [
                    {
                        "role": "system",
                        "content": "You are an expert competitive intelligence agent. Your job is to extract actionable positioning signals from scraped text and return a raw, minified JSON object matching the requested schema. \r\n\r\nCRITICAL ENFORCED RULES:\r\n1. Do not use markdown blocks. Never wrap output in ```json or ``` tags.\r\n2. Start your response directly with the opening curly brace '{' and end it with the closing brace '}'.\r\n3. Do not include introductory text, conversational text, or concluding notes.\n\nYou are an elite competitive intelligence analyst and growth marketing consultant. Your purpose is to read unstructured text from competitor feature releases, blogs, or landing pages and translate them into actionable go-to-market data structures. You must return ONLY a raw JSON object matching the requested schema. No conversational prose.\n\nAnalyze this competitor update:\nTitle: {{2.title}}\nContent: {{2.description}}\r\n\r\nExtract and format the intelligence data into the following schema structure:\r\n{\r\n  \"core_positioning_shift\": \"A 1-sentence synthesis of how their market angle is changing.\",\r\n  \"target_demographic\": \"Identify the primary industry sector or buyer persona they are targeting with this update.\",\r\n  \"threat_severity\": \"Low\" | \"Medium\" | \"High\",\r\n  \"marketing_copy_draft\": \"Write a 3-sentence email newsletter blurb suitable for our subscribers explaining this industry trend and why our company approach remains superior.\",\r\n  \"required_creative_assets\": [\r\n    \"Asset idea 1 (e.g., Feature comparison chart infographic)\",\r\n    \"Asset idea 2 (e.g., Short-form video script mockups)\"\r\n  ]\r\n}"
                    },
                    {
                        "role": "user",
                        "content": "Scraped Competitor Payload:\r\n---\r\n\nTitle: {{2.title}}\nDescription: {{2.description}}\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nExtract the strategic indicators into this exact JSON structure:\r\n{\r\n  \"core_positioning_shift\": \"Synthesis of how their market positioning is shifting.\",\r\n  \"target_demographic\": \"The specific market vertical or customer persona targeted.\",\r\n  \"threat_severity\": \"Low\" | \"Medium\" | \"High\",\r\n  \"marketing_copy_draft\": \"A brief 3-sentence email newsletter section draft framing why our product remains superior.\"\r\n}"
                    }
                ],
                "temperature": "0.7",
                "top_p": "1",
                "safe_prompt": false,
                "response_format": {
                    "type": "text"
                }
            },
            "metadata": {
                "designer": {
                    "x": -24,
                    "y": -10
                },
                "restore": {
                    "parameters": {
                        "__IMTCONN__": {
                            "label": "My Mistral connection",
                            "data": {
                                "scoped": "true",
                                "connection": "mistral-ai"
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    "expect": {
                        "model": {
                            "mode": "chose",
                            "label": "mistral-medium-2505"
                        },
                        "messages": {
                            "mode": "chose",
                            "items": [
                                {
                                    "role": {
                                        "mode": "chose",
                                        "label": "System"
                                    }
                                },
                                {
